5.Directives are instruction for VueJS to do things in a certain way.

v-html:Update the element's innerHTML.
v-for:Render the element or template block multiple times based on the source data.
v-on:Attach an event listener to the element.
v-text:Update the element's text content.
v-model:Create a two-way binding on a form input element or a component.
v-once:to preserve initial value and it will be only evaluated once





4.Event:-
1. v-on:click
2. v-on:submit
3. v-on:scroll
4. v-on:keyup
5. v-on:change
6. v-on:mouseover
7. v-on:mouseout
8. v-on:input
